{"tid":1382353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣］與其拉攏台灣，不如拉攏....","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:09:09.000Z","uid":292743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45b55182ff36fc85ae4db1169b5c421fe15d622c","tid":1382353,"uid":292743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"反其道而行，應該拉攏強國13 億人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結比送中更可怕</span><br />\n<br />\n我地要將訴求變成所有大陸人都同意，咁樣再鬧下去就會影響到中國政權，共狗一定會搵人祭旗。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">必須要拿下鄧炳強</span><br />\n<br />\n要聚焦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反黑除惡，嚴查保護傘</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要全世界，特別係中國知道香港被巨大警黑保護傘亂政，要迫佢地交人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先除官黑勾結，爭取公平法冶，之後一切好辦</span>，否則黑警長期違法打人，多多義士都唔夠抽。"},{"pid":"4c3c5336276d86927e0336ce605a237bca53f431","tid":1382353,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"04ef6432d13d3867eb95c66735cce0655d729d41","tid":1382353,"uid":187972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"問題主要係70%大陸人冇腦"},{"pid":"bd3712c71f86d6273e16ad00dd111c067988c32c","tid":1382353,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"泛民做左三十年啦"},{"pid":"8f20ecd9d08a4a64d88c9f1631a5c62deb91cf93","tid":1382353,"uid":292743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔使理佢地有冇腦，我地要將標題變成全世界都贊成，包括藍屍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聚焦係堅守一國兩制，反黑除惡，嚴查保護傘。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邀請建制派出席支持，先迫佢地表態，佢哋冇得唔支持呢個習帝叫開既口號。再推去獨立調查委員會</span></span>"},{"pid":"f551a23b23b45